author: cms-sw
body:
Following externals are now used from cms externals distribution for building TF. We can also use `eigen` from cms externals but currently the eigen version we have in cmsdist is bit newer then the one needed by TF (so TF failed to build with our version). We need to sync these versions so that TF can use our verison of eigen
 
 - png
 - jpeg
 - zlib
- curl
 - protobuf
 - pcre
 - gif
 - sqlite3
 - swig
 - cython
 - py2-functools32
 - py2-enum34
 - py2-astor
 - py2-six
 - py2-absl_py
 - py2-termcolor
 - py2-keras_applications
 - py2-pasta
 - py2-wrapt
 - py2-gast
 - py2-backports_weakref
 - py2-opt_einsum
title: [TF] Update TF to version 2.1 using externals from cms distribution
